records.text: OTDTE is an intelligence company founded by alique ,
to focus on the understanding and development of the mind.
as a society we can all learn to use our minds to achieve even
greater heights than what we have done thus far. It's our
belief that We all have the potential to collectively use our
minds to solve the biggest of problems and to shape a better
reality for all of us. It's up to us as a community to make the
most of the gift that was given to us, The Mind.
At OTDTE, We're developing apps and games
with the sole intent of mind stimulation.
Games already provide varying degrees of
stimulation but we want to focus on
offering optimal mind stimulaton, as well as
providing information on how the app or
game is intended to stimulate the mind.
